        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "3. **Executive Director Opening Remarks** – Ms. Harris reported it is day 94 of working virtually due to COVID-19. She noted the Regional Coordinators have been making regular contact with the PSAPs. One PSAP had to execute their backup plan for cleaning due to a positive COVID-19 employee. On May 20, Mitchell County was the first ESInet migrated PSAP since COVID-19 restrictions began They were the 37th PSAP migrated."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "4. **May 14, 2020 Meeting Minutes Approval** – Motion by Glen Knox, seconded by Jude O'Sullivan. Approved unanimously by roll call vote."
        },
